title: The Killing of Freddie Gray – Episode 11 - Autopsy
description:
May 22, 2017 / The autopsy report limited the possibilities for Freddie Gray’s fatal injury. But what information was the medical examiner using to make her determinations?

Episode scoring music by AnimalWeapon, Blue Dot Sessions, Chris Zabriskie, Fleslit, H-LR, Jahzzar, Remain, Uncanny Valleys, VYVCH, and Sym5.
